% TODO (by DaHe) Although it is shown in the code above, it might also be a
% good idea to explain in words that idx, expx, sinx, and cosx are the functions
% id, exp, sin, and cos expressed as power series. It could also be mentioned
% that you need to define both sinx and cosx in order to evaluate either of
% them, since there is a circular dependency between them.
